            Data from table 3.
HISTORY    (20180301U) Corrected by SD and VV: STATUS.
           (20260113U) Corrected by V.Varlamov: EN-SEC, STATUS.
ENDBIB               5
COMMON               1          3
ANG
ADEG
   70.
ENDCOMMON            3
